{"ud3.9:0.1":"Udana 3.9 ","ud3.9:0.2":"Sippasutta ","ud3.9:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","ud3.9:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","ud3.9:1.3":"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulanam bhikkhunam pacchabhattam pindapatapatikkantanam mandalamale sannisinnanam sannipatitanam ayamantarakatha udapadi: ","ud3.9:1.4":"“ko nu kho, avuso, sippam janati? ","ud3.9:1.5":"Ko kim sippam sikkhi? ","ud3.9:1.6":"Kataram sippam sippanam aggan”ti? ","ud3.9:2.1":"Tatthekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.2":"“hatthisippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.3":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.4":"“assasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.5":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.6":"“rathasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.7":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.8":"“dhanusippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.9":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.10":"“tharusippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.11":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.12":"“muddasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.13":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.14":"“gananasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.15":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.16":"“sankhanasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.17":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.18":"“lekhasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.19":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.20":"“kaveyyasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.21":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.22":"“lokayatasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.23":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:2.24":"“khattavijjasippam sippanam aggan”ti. ","ud3.9:2.25":"Ayancarahi tesam bhikkhunam antarakatha hoti vippakata. ","ud3.9:3.1":"Atha kho bhagava sayanhasamayam patisallana vutthito yena mandalamalo tenupasankami; upasankamitva pannatte asane nisidi. ","ud3.9:3.2":"Nisajja kho bhagava bhikkhu amantesi: ","ud3.9:3.3":"“kaya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathaya sannisinna, ka ca pana vo antarakatha vippakata”ti? ","ud3.9:4.1":"“Idha, bhante, amhakam pacchabhattam pindapatapatikkantanam mandalamale sannisinnanam ayamantarakatha udapadi: ","ud3.9:4.2":"‘ko nu kho, avuso, sippam janati? ","ud3.9:4.3":"Ko kim sippam sikkhi? ","ud3.9:4.4":"Kataram sippam sippanam aggan’ti? ","ud3.9:5.1":"Tatthekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.2":"‘hatthisippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.3":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.4":"‘assasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.5":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.6":"‘rathasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.7":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.8":"‘dhanusippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.9":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.10":"‘tharusippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.11":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.12":"‘muddasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.13":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.14":"‘gananasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.15":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.16":"‘sankhanasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.17":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.18":"‘lekhasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.19":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.20":"‘kaveyyasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.21":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.22":"‘lokayatasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.23":"Ekacce evamahamsu: ","ud3.9:5.24":"‘khattavijjasippam sippanam aggan’ti. ","ud3.9:5.25":"Ayam kho no, bhante, antarakatha hoti vippakata, atha bhagava anuppatto”ti. ","ud3.9:6.1":"“Na khvetam, bhikkhave, tumhakam patirupam kulaputtanam saddha agarasma anagariyam pabbajitanam yam tumhe evarupim katham katheyyatha. ","ud3.9:6.2":"Sannipatitanam vo, bhikkhave, dvayam karaniyam—","ud3.9:6.3":"dhammi va katha ariyo va tunhibhavo”ti. ","ud3.9:7.1":"Atha kho bhagava etamattham viditva tayam velayam imam udanam udanesi: ","ud3.9:8.1":"“Asippajivi lahu atthakamo, ","ud3.9:8.2":"Yatindriyo sabbadhi vippamutto; ","ud3.9:8.3":"Anokasari amamo niraso, ","ud3.9:8.4":"Hitva manam ekacaro sa bhikkhu”ti. ","ud3.9:8.5":"Navamam. "}